high_descs: Turn to the right then walk forward. Turn right and face the shelving unit.
Pick up the spoon from the shelf.
Turn to the right then turn to the left and face the sink.
Place the spoon in the sink and wash it. Drain the water and then take out the spoon.
Turn around completely and walk to the left. Turn to the right and face the shelf again.
Place the spoon on the shelf again.
anns.task_desc: Wash the spoon in the sink.

high_descs: Walk forward, then turn right and walk across the room to the white table, then turn right and walk up to the small black shelving unit.
Pick up the metal spoon off of the small black shelving unit.
Turn right and walk over to the sink.
Wash the spoon in the sink and then take it out.
Turn around and walk forward, then turn right and walk over to the white table, turn right again to face the black shelving unit.
Put the clean spoon on top of the black shelving unit.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean spoon on a black shelving unit.

high_descs: Turn right and walk to the small black table in the corner to your right.
Pick up the spoon on the small black table.
Look up and walk to the sink to your right and look down.
Place the spoon in the sink, wash it and remove it from the sink.
Take the spoon, turn around, turn right and walk to the small black table to your right.
Place the clean spoon on the small black table.
anns.task_desc: Place a clean spoon on the small black table.
